trans-unit.source: Defines the abstract base class for composable parts, which import objects and produce exported objects.
trans-unit.target: Define a classe base abstrata para partes combináveis, que importam objetos e produzem objetos exportados.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: Called when all the imports of the part have been set, and exports can be retrieved.
trans-unit.target: Chamado quando todas as importações da parte tiverem sido definidas e as exportações puderem ser recuperadas.

trans-unit.source: Once this method is called, no further imports can be set unless a call is made to Deactivate.
trans-unit.target: Quando este método é chamado, não importa adicional pode ser definida, a menos que uma chamada é feita para desativar.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the exported objects provided by the part.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção dos objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> que descrevem os objetos exportados fornecidos pela parte.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the exported objects provided by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objetos que descrevem os objetos exportados fornecidos pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ExportDefinitions%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto foi criado de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propriedade deve retornar o resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ExportDefinitions%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not have exports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> não tem exportações, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> coleção em vez disso.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> foi descartado.

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects from the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> property that describes the exported object to return.
trans-unit.target: Um dos objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> da propriedade <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> que descreve o objeto exportado a ser retornado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the exported object described by the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto exportado descrito pelo objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The exported object described by <paramref name="definition" />.
trans-unit.target: O objeto exportado descrito por <paramref name="definition" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> foi descartado.

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="definition" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred getting the exported object described by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Ocorreu um erro ao obter o objeto exportado descrito pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="definition" /> did not originate from the <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> property on the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="definition" /> não se originaram na propriedade <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart.ExportDefinitions" /> no <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: One or more prerequisite imports, indicated by <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition.IsPrerequisite" />, have not been set.
trans-unit.target: Uma ou mais importações de pré-requisitos, indicadas por <see cref="P:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition.IsPrerequisite" />, não foram definidas.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imported objects required by the part.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção dos objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> que descrevem os objetos importados exigidos pela parte.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imported objects required by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objetos que descrevem os objetos importados necessários para o <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ImportDefinitions%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto foi criado de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propriedade deve retornar o resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.ImportDefinitions%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> não tem importações, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> coleção em vez disso.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> foi descartado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os metadados do objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: The metadata of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Os metadados da <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é vazio, somente leitura <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object was created from a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> object, this property should return the result of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.Metadata%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto foi criado de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> de objeto, esta propriedade deve retornar o resultado de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition.Metadata%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade devem retornar somente leitura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objeto com uma comparação não linguística, diferencia maiusculas de minúsculas, como <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>e nunca deve retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> não contém metadados, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> em vez disso.

trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> foi descartado.
